Squizzy::
She listened to Feline tell her story. "Hold on a nano," she said and 
took the samples of DNA from Diamond. "Thank you Diamond," she said 
as Diamond left the lab.  She turned to Feline,"OK, your still in 
good shape, we jst have to give you another beast mode. Any ideas?"

Feline::
She shook her head no. "Nope."

Squizzy::
"OK then, follow me."  She lead Feline to the console and showed her 
every kind of cat DNA she had on record.  After a few minutes, Feline 
showed Squizzy just which new beast mode she wanted.  Squizzy then 
put Feline into a CR tank and started to download the programs and 
inserted the correct DNA into the regeneration fluid.  It would take 
a few hours, but when she was finished, Feline would be a new bot. In 
the mean time, Squizzy to the DNA samples and started to anylize, 
catagorize and sort them all out.
